{"tid":1691692,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"終於明白點解將軍澳尚德戰鬥力咁勁","createTime":"2019-11-03T18:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T22:45:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":914,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"e903f871b3a6c2d7bb370ef1cd777b132664585d","tid":1691692,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20160331/large/a1101a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20160331%2Flarge%2Fa1101a.gif&h=c3d26a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦的十大票站，其中9個票站90後的選民比例高逾12%，較整個新界東的11.5%平均水平為高，而此9個票站均是整個新界東首三成最多90後的選區。<br />\n值得留意的是梁天琦最高得票選區將軍澳公屋尚德邨，此區的選民組成極具特色，該區的90後選民比例高達23.1%，一舉力壓其他年齡組群，該區40後選民為13.5%，50後選民為20%，60後選民則為21.5%；而這個90後力壓其他年齡組群情況，全港幾乎絕無僅有。除了尚德區，僅天水圍天恒區出現。但是無論尚德區或天恒區，區選卻由建制派工聯會的候選人勝出。"},{"pid":"7c6853c6d0c3ecc271f80ff3d09509d368491131","tid":1691692,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:23:23.000Z","msg":"甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[日常文宣] [文宣方向] 以子之矛，攻子之盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0b35d640797f9827c4228ecf15c41089a37f03b","tid":1691692,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0769272d6a66e46782bcc479007585ece8b477c8","tid":1691692,"uid":12773,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T18:43:05.000Z","msg":"必須立即坐言起行<br />\n講得出做得到<br />\n新口號<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還拖</span></span><br />\n<br />\n每時每刻帶備長傘<br />\n打狗救人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我宣佈，唔好再鳩叫香港人反抗，要叫香港人還拖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1690541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1690541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4e02ce5f837a7ba26bc6c14f6a107d76c4e58d81","tid":1691692,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ded1086c3cf5a51f6ad09c02a05b84e297d3dc","tid":1691692,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:00:01.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"bda81ca19b6a237e74aaf5bd7557960b4ad96c6c","tid":1691692,"uid":49781,"like":141,"dislike":2,"score":139,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:01:21.000Z","msg":"咁又唔完全係尚德人來嘅<br />\n好多都係將軍澳其他區入來<br />\n不過將軍澳好多90 00後嘅人係到長大<br />\n同時亦存在好多藍屍廢老"},{"pid":"a9f899922aa4da75f504efbed38c3dfbb65fe08c","tid":1691692,"uid":294,"like":99,"dislike":4,"score":95,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"因為尚德有間迪卡儂呀"},{"pid":"a06e47309f13689e1f09efa8f5ed24f71054639d","tid":1691692,"uid":53666,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:03:28.000Z","msg":"新首都"},{"pid":"dd3ff11b636a179ed3c08d9aade56768266e1345","tid":1691692,"uid":121197,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:03:41.000Z","msg":"2016年新東補選天琦唯一票站得票高過楊岳橋嘅就係尚德<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6c998c3291ab7efa186107bab0dcd502966aa7","tid":1691692,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:04:38.000Z","msg":"首都"},{"pid":"3c5399154162c348b885d99aa034ce93c2eb275a","tid":1691692,"uid":130563,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:06:24.000Z","msg":"唔好拎呢樣野打飛機喇，西貢區區選基本上建制全勝，包括尚德<br />\n尚德尋日個2號派咗全日傳單，聽到好多阿嬸阿叔對佢非常認同...<br />\n大家努力啦。"},{"pid":"9ebab45375c472f164c5f2659457ba20c5fca00f","tid":1691692,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:07:05.