r />\n尚德尋日個2號派咗全日傳單，聽到好多阿嬸阿叔對佢非常認同...<br />\n大家努力啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"呢個真<br />\n唔好再睇錯形勢啦"},{"pid":"03c09c4a26fc9905ed4940c096a52b05f5b3df72","tid":1691692,"uid":57438,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:14:50.000Z","msg":"尚德係重蝗區<br />\n仲要係福建蝗<br />\n廣東話都唔識兩句<br />\n公屋互委會其實福建同鄉會<br />\n日日排飯<br />\n尚德手足可以去排下餵狗<br />\n(唔該好戲啲, 鬧下暴徒呀, 屌下啲後生咁)<br />\n<br />\n廣明區議員莊XX<br />\n個區乜Q 都唔理<br />\n淨係識得氹啲貪小便宜廢老<br />\n<br />\n最癲係有老人院有庇護工場<br />\n一選舉就一車車輪椅推啲你會懷疑佢地能力嘅老人/病人投票<br />\n好恐怖的"},{"pid":"cd063e3ceef8f79e9dd0b1d7f954002125482d99","tid":1691692,"uid":218468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:38:33.000Z","msg":"尚德好野！"},{"pid":"2f90dc18e031de6cac4b70e449984e34d7575184","tid":1691692,"uid":277851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037bbbb4908828266fb276f89cc5e2bf58093235","tid":1691692,"uid":76421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:40:23.000Z","msg":"將軍澳，黃浦，太古<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f939601c85da4c9424cf153b39e21a64b6f3457f","tid":1691692,"uid":1874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fc2f9bb569d683e8f9c814c7d9b1c16f691d432","tid":1691692,"uid":53673,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:08:47.000Z","msg":"但個區議會議席係建制派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚頂癮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:40:57.000Z","msg":"光頭簡唔知今年可唔可以收皮"},{"pid":"0816b899d5c7be1ea16fd086b6a1fa470f47fd4c","tid"