f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />號稱首都既沙田當年係咪投撚曬關鍵一席？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"2016年天琦好落力喺沙田拉票<br />\n可惜好多人都仲係要大局為重投咗7號<br />\n結果佢大選喺新城市擺檔攞提名時啲人排長龍提名佢"},{"pid":"9d69663a62cb3ea5cd9d371e0c739dc7ffa361ea","tid":1691692,"uid":86071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9f899922aa4da75f504efbed38c3dfbb65fe08c","tid":1691692,"uid":294,"like":99,"dislike":4,"score":95,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"因為尚德有間迪卡儂呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"又唔見銅鑼灣同旺角咁高戰鬥力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88fac952ef0a5aca0da4c16f539cdf9c0ff8f75","tid":1691692,"uid":550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:58:21.000Z","msg":"尚德入伙住到而家想講兩句<br />\n16年補選點解天琦喺度撼低關鍵一席<br />\n係因為邨內只有鼎鼎同護琦手拉票<br />\n泛民班友怕撚咗尚德結界唔敢入<br />\n有啲唔睇新聞嘅中間派 就係咁投咗比天琦<br />\n年齡分佈呢區好兩極 後生同廢老都多<br />\n次次投票都係老坑區同Y字頭身份證排長龍"},{"pid":"4e8c18e56360a1cdfa3a321f04fb86f2e33115fc","tid":1691692,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:01:42.000Z","msg":"共享單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca149f38daaea7fb595a0ce36c63711409feab5f","tid":1691692,"uid":237581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"【二百萬三罷聯合陣線】<br />\n大家怨完呻完，想罷工，想了解點實行嘅，<br />\n可以入Channel參考吓。<br />\n成日話得我罷有咩用，咁俾多啲人都了解吓吖。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️常見問題⚠️<br />\n1. 幾時罷工呀？<br />\n其實罷工有好多前期準備工作，唔係定個日子就可以罷。一來要處理錢嘅問題，需要有罷工基金support，而罷工基金往往係由工會處理返自己個行業。二來要處理邊際成本嘅問題，例如成間公司得一個人罷，甚至有藍絲篤灰，老闆要炒話咁易，但如果成間公司有一半人罷工就好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n2. 咁點樣處理上述講嘅問題？<br />\n罷工好多時會有前期嘅行業行動，例如搵一日係網上call支持罷工嘅人集體dress code或者一齊戴朵花，又或者85三罷前嘅行業集會，咁你就可以由網絡延伸到real contact，知道實質你所處嘅職場有幾多係自己人，繼而組成組織，由自己working place去到隔離公司，甚至成個地區或行業。另一個方法就係工會，以成為會員嘅方式組成real contact，再用工會名義發起罷工。<br />\n<br />\n3. 我可以做啲咩？<br />\n幫手reach你自己行業嘅人，或者參與成立你所屬行業嘅工會。仲有share呢個群組出去，等呢度可以凝聚到更多有意有心罷工嘅人。<br />\n成立工會程序可參照 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F63&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=8b945b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/63</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 罷工基金點搞好？<br />\n目前主要有兩種聲音，一係眾籌，二係工會自己搞返自己行業嘅罷工基金。前者問題在於好難確認申請人係咪真係參與罷工定呃基金，而且如果個個行業人人都申請得，要處理極龐大嘅行政以及法律程序。相較之下，如果工會處理自身罷工基金可以免卻基金被濫用嘅問題，因為要會員先可以申請。當然，基金仍然需要好多討論。<br />\n<br />\n5. 呢個群組有咩用？<br />\n再次強調每個行業嘅組織、籌備工會或者工業行動要返返去自己個行業嗰度傾。但正因為行業太多，每個情況都唔同，所以呢個群組可以俾大家互通消息，最快知道各個行業嘅情況。同埋俾有心搞三罷嘅人可以係度集中討論。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️現設以下分台⚠️<br />\n三罷文宣小組 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=9275cdda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OUHilRRJw8V58N8AmwOrYw</a><br />\n罷工基金討論台 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkstrikefund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstrikefund&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=b048b212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstrikefund</a><br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會  | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=f215885f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n公海 <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=a44d75b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FhM2GRbY1ThsEzrnbEyduA</a><br />\n(必讀)群組須知及group list <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/61\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F61&d=JjpB%2FqIgFksXGEBY%2BN5axOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=4e550337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/61</a>"},{"pid":"23dd4714063922bd386eac75735e2a136ae9bdf5","tid":1691692,"uid":45502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W67GHcU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW67GHcU.jpg&h=da633307&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c20db2aba593c3bb980229cfd5d30bd90aa831b","tid":1691692,"uid":107687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9fdc028176fedbfef0c43f3594117d657b6c17","tid":1691692,"uid":130563,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"15367e7f29f2f447ab5d07817f49e1247e66a80b","tid":1691692,"uid":294,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"8f7e023fcf6cb04f98ffb492e27b5a8686ef8ee2","tid":1691692,"uid":130563,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:07:09.000Z","msg":"開張冇耐咋喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:08:33.000Z","msg":"但都比人掃哂貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"佢而架乜都冇貨<br />\n想買條橡筋帶做運動都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890b675c7126b214361cec4febdfb05e080768dc","tid":1691692,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:02:30.000Z","msg":"但呢個區啲區議會選舉 民賤聯大勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eafd645205f6329182f66e2b559013bb560a7bd","tid":1691692,"uid":252862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ebab45375c472f164c5f2659457ba20c5fca00f","tid":1691692,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:07:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:04:23.000Z","msg":"尚德與將軍澳聯合同在<im